data.description: Beautiful Cozy and modern home in the Mission Ridge neighborhood. Close to parks (minutes in walking distance) 3 bedrooms. Spacious Master bedroom. Master Bathroom with two granite sink, Bathtub and separate Shower with 2 shower heads. Walk-in Closet. Half bathroom with bathtub and granite sink. Open floor plan with full functional Kitchen. Granite countertops on the entire Kitchen and island. Beautiful developed backyard with pergola and has a good view of the Lartington Park. Solar Panels are not paid off as of list date. Balance is approximately 20,000 and monthly payment is $112. Buyer would have to get pre-approved for the solar panel loan.
